{
  "stem": "11641.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And after Rosh Hashanah, he came home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I still didn't have knowledge of my mother and my brother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So after a month or so, we got a message that their train was bombed also when they went.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were re-routed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they went back home where we lived before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they stood there-- a lot of people stood there-- and they waited.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then there came a-- an order to all the male Jews, clear the area of Upper Silesia and go to Russian border.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And under penalty of shooting, they have to cross the border to Russia.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother found out about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she rented sort of a truck, loaded whatever she could on it, and came to us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's December 19-- November or December 1939.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She came, and we were together as a family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A lot of our friends, my friends, were in Russia during the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this came some good sort of so to speak, but they were forced to go to-- to Russia, and they remained there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Two of my uncles, my mother's two brothers, you know, happened to be the same way in Russia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At-- at this point, my family was at my-- my aunt's house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- in Klaj.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The name was K-L-A-J in Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "K-L-A-J.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Polish, name was Klaj, it was written.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It is-- was in a-- It was a-- in a village.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But there was not enough room for all of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So my mother-- my father had a brother in Stary Wisnicz where actually my grandfather used to live before he passed away.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said, look, I can rent you a room-- you know, a nominal fee, rent you a room.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You come there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we went there to live.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
